> An interactive **Microsoft Excel Dashboard** built using **Pivot Tables, Pivot Charts, Slicers, and Excel Data Analysis tools** to analyze coffee sales performance and identify business trends. The dashboard provides an easy-to-understand overview of sales by coffee type, payment method, and time period. ([Nathan Ayers][1])

