# 📊 Project Overview

This project analyzes coffee shop sales data using Microsoft Excel. The dashboard allows users to interactively explore sales trends through slicers and dynamic charts.

The objective is to:

* ☕ Analyze coffee sales
* 📅 Track monthly sales performance
* 💰 Compare payment methods
* 📈 Identify top-selling coffee products
* 🎯 Create an interactive business dashboard

---

# 🗂 Dataset Information

The dataset contains coffee sales transaction records.

### 📌 Columns Used

| Column        | Description                |
| ------------- | -------------------------- |
| 📅 Date       | Transaction Date           |
| ☕ Coffee Name | Name of coffee sold        |
| 💵 Money      | Sales Amount               |
| 💳 Cash Type  | Payment Method (Cash/Card) |

---

# 📈 Dashboard Features

### ☕ Sales by Coffee Type

* Displays sales for each coffee product.
* Helps identify:

  * ⭐ Best-selling coffee
  * 📉 Low-performing coffee

---

### 📅 Sales by Month

Shows monthly sales trends.

Benefits:

* Seasonal analysis
* Monthly comparison
* Business growth tracking

---

### 💳 Payment Method Analysis

Compares

* 💵 Cash
* 💳 Card

Useful for understanding customer payment preferences.

---

### 🎛 Interactive Filters (Slicers)

Dashboard includes filters for:

* 📅 Month
* 📆 Day
* ☕ Coffee Name
* 💵 Sales Amount
* 💳 Payment Type

Users can dynamically filter every chart.

